|-
! ''k'' !! 点估计值 !! 置信区间
|-
|  1 ||    <math>\scriptstyle 2m</math> ||   <math>\scriptstyle [m,\, 20m]</math>
|-
|  2 ||  <math>\scriptstyle 1.5m</math> ||  <math>\scriptstyle [m,\, 4.5m]</math>
|-
|  5 ||  <math>\scriptstyle 1.2m</math> || <math>\scriptstyle [m,\, 1.82m]</math>
|-
